text.tspan: Emissions of air pollutants, United Kingdom
Annual emissions of various air pollutants, indexed to emission levels in 1970 (or 1980 in the case of ammonia).
Values in 1970 (1980 for ammonia) are normalised to 100; values below 100 therefore indicate a decline in
emissions. Volatile organic compounds (VOCs) do not include methane emissions.
